com.SIMRacingApps

Class Session.CarIdentifiers

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.SIMRacingApps.Session.CarIdentifiers
  • Enclosing class:
    Session

    public static final class Session.CarIdentifiers
extends java.lang.Object
    This class enumerates the various car identifiers. Dynamic identifiers are the ones where additional information is appended, such as, the position, the number, etc. This is provided as a convenience to prevent type-os. See Session.getCar(String)
